static ConditionalDistribution DistributionFactory.upgradeCPD(ConditionalDistribution distribution)
          Generates a CPD that basically can contain the largest diversity of variable mixes given the current distribution, this means that for continuous variables we are going to end up with a LinearGaussianMix for now, discrete variables probably should not use this right away, as right now they just return the distribution that they were already a part of.

          Distribution for a continuous variable with only discrete parents
 class LinearGaussian
          Distribution for continuous variable with only continuous parents, this is linear in the sense that the mean is a linear combination of each parent value.
 class LinearGaussianMix
          Distribution for a continuous variable that has both discrete and continuous parents.

          This handles a generalized mixture of discrete and continuous components
 class MultinomialSigmoid
          This is a distribution for a discrete variable that has continuous parents
 class MultinomialSigmoidMix
